title: Pro Samples - 50,000 Sound samples and FX
description:
A MUST HAVE for producers and DJ&#039;s alike. Hundreds of Drumkits, FX, and instrument packs make up this collection, covering all sorts of genres, like Hip-Hop and Trance.

Here are a few of the packs included:
Modern Beat (all kits)
Free J Dilla
24bit Sidechainer
Urban Warfare FX (in .wav and .aiff format)
East Coast Drum Library
Philharmonia Samples
Lead Rock
JR Soundfonts

& Much, much more!

Also included is MagicISO, a freeware program that will allow you to mount the disc image.

PLEASE SEED!


-DjN
